data.description: Discover the charm of this spacious single-story gem with in-law quarters potential. Located in the family-oriented Portofino Lakes community, this property awaits your personal touch. TLC needed, but imagine the possibilities for customization. With a well-planned layout and the added perk of in-law quarters, this home offers flexibility and convenience. The safe and welcoming neighborhood enhances the appeal, perfect for family living. Bring your toothbrush and transform this canvas into your dream home. Schedule a tour today and seize the opportunity of this awesome property!
